{"tid":1372790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門]全民運動週 大家一齊做運動","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:52:55.000Z","uid":228656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"735f696cc9db29f0c51032190c570aeb8b8f9020","tid":1372790,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"眾所周知香港男人行路喘氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論男定女都好成日都要返工返學真係好少做運動<br />\n不過唔緊要全民運動日都就嚟黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8月4就係全民運動日<br />\n既然政府咁想市民健康做多啲運動咁我哋就提前呢幾排開始做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左羽毛球 仲有咩運動適合到全港十八區打呢?<br />\n今日介紹一款 滾軸曲棍球 男女老幼都啱打<br />\n當敵軍打到黎逃走速度又快<br />\n但係要小心唔好勾到人哋粒蛋拆人祠堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者打到人哋小腿骨同埋波羅蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為咁樣就犯規啦<br />\n咁安全果方面就係要戴晒護膝嗰啲啦仲有最緊要嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">頭盔</span></span><br />\n挽運動要好好保護自己經常小心安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有冇連登娘子軍同我一齊打呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齊創健康香港 有賴你我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40623430d860f3a6db78264af949bd8643afaf93","tid":1372790,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"33c4db04879bc94454fb8b5e5ced5dfd5274a23a","tid":1372790,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"96960d5bee0705e765247d2370f3d089f9ce99af","tid":1372790,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"680b54cd40f63f1cee104477c6178f1bdc2ba810","tid":1372790,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"2430c5c1ed4